    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In His plan, He formed man, who surveyed all that God had made."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "While he ached for a mate, for a counterpart."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Man could taste the e’ternal yearning that so long in God was burning!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Eve was built from Adam’s side, And his heart was satisfied;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Told the story of the hidden heart of God."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But when Eve was deceived, what was pure fell beyond a cure;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All creation enslaved under vanity!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God was born in human hist’ry, To reveal its greatest myst’ry!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That the answer for the earth was that Christ so loved the church;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He would die to satisfy the heart of God."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So alone this grain dies, but with joy to obtain His prize."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And with life both divine and unbreakable!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He arises, powers hear it! He will court her as the Spirit!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Blood and water from His side will redeem and build His bride,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "She will satisfy the riven heart of God."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When He breathed she received His divine personality;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Flowing in, washing sin, death and age away."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So that He might sanctify her by the washing of the water;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Adding beauty, adding health, to present her to Himself:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Full of glory for the holy heart of God."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In a time beyond time, in an age beyond the ages;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God and man will be one for eternity."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah! What a story! She is brought from gloom to glory!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And the longing from the start, for a bride, a counterpart,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is fulfilled inside the happy heart of God!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
